name: DaWae
description: DAWAE: The Meme Coin That Knows the Way Straight outta the depths of internet legend, DAWAE is here to lead the next meme revolution on the Ethereum blockchain. Inspired by the legendary Ugandan Knuckles and the timeless phrase “Do you know da wae?”, DAWAE is more than just a coin — it’s a movement for trolls, degens, and meme connoisseurs alike. We’re bringing the raw, unfiltered energy of viral internet culture to Web3. DAWAE isn’t just about laughs — it’s about community, chaos, and crypto-powered fun. Built for those who know de wae, and powered by those bold enough to follow it.
